<span style="font-weight: 400;">According to her, the main cause of endometriosis is: </span><b>Insecurity, disappointment and frustration. Replacing self-love with sugar. Blamers.</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">One of the ways of healing this is through saying or writing affirmations.¬†</span>

